<div dir=3D"auto">Hi Richard,
<div><br>
</div>
<div>Tower is piling everything into the general repair and replacement prov=
isions of schedule 1 and saying they=E2=80=99re not complete or substantial.=
 That exemption aspect is debatable in regards to a few floor joists maybe.<=
/div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>Tower are however not acknowledging/ignoring the other parts of schedul=
e 1 that aren=E2=80=99t exempted and that I have referred to and referenced i=
n my report regarding load bearing walls, wall bracing, wall insulation and t=
he deck that is greater than 1.5m in
 height.</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>Happy to discuss next week.</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>Kind regards&nbsp;</div>
<div>Josh</div>
