<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The=
 updated scope-of-works attached has been created as a proposed inclusive re=
sponse to the findings of all the documents attached.</span></p>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Whi=
le you are reviewing the attachments, I would like to propose that I begin t=
he process of obtaining repair proposals from Tower approved builders to pro=
gress the claim as quickly as possible.</span></p>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">If I=
 send out the scope of works now and offer to meet with the tender responden=
ts onsite, we may well have some preliminary costings to hand prior to the e=
nd of the business year.</span></p>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Ple=
ase confirm your approval for me to begin the process of preliminary pricing=
 now.</span></p>
