<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nb=
sp;</span></p>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Pri=
or to receiving the report from the forensic testing =E2=80=93 I am keen to t=
ake whatever steps I can to progress the claim.</span></p>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Pre=
liminary results and findings suggest that we may have a relatively complete=
