he property under the claim.</span></p>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nb=
sp;</span></p>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">If w=
e accept on a preliminary basis that the scope of works required to remediat=
