<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We e=
xpect the test results to be available to share with all parties by the end o=
f next week. I have chased the provider to expedite this.
</span></p>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The=
 preliminary report from the Forensic Testing will contain the =E2=80=98raw d=
ata=E2=80=99 from the laboratory results, and the locations of the sample si=
tes from where the tests were conducted.</span></p>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As p=
romised this preliminary report will be shared with all as soon as it is rec=
eived and it will be followed by a fuller report which will provide Towers p=
osition on the findings of the report.</span></p>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Tha=
nk you for your continued patience.</span></p>
