<ol start=3D"1" type=3D"1" style=3D"margin-top:0cm">
<li class=3D"x_MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm; margin-bottom:0cm"=
><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">That the chlorine was locat=
ed in the laundry room downstairs at the time of the fire.</span><span lang=3D=
