is.Cornwall@tower.co.nz">Chris.Cornwall@tower.co.nz</a>&gt;;
 Megan Jensen &lt;<a href=3D"mailto:Megan.Jensen@tower.co.nz">Megan.Jensen@t=
ower.co.nz</a>&gt;<br>
<b>Subject:</b><span class=3D"x_apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>Re: C903=
06048 - Fire at 23 Mays Street, Devonport [WW-ACTIVE.FID3167762]</span><span=
 lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:1.0pt; colo=
r:white">Kia ora Grant, Thank you for your email and for confirming receipt o=
f our letter. Friday, 17 October after 2:</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D=
"font-size:1.0pt; font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif; color:white">=E2=
=80=8A</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:1.0pt; color:white">00
 pm works for me, and I=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment co=
uld be scheduled accordingly. I also reserve my right to undertake</span><sp=
an lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:1.0pt; colo=
r:white">&nbsp;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Kia ora Grant,</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Thank you for your email and f=
or confirming receipt of our letter.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Friday, 17 October after 2:00 p=
m works for me, and I=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment coul=
d be scheduled accordingly.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I also reserve my right to und=
ertake independent testing and assessment of the property to ensure a full a=
nd impartial evaluation.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Having reviewed the proposed p=
lan, I=E2=80=99m concerned the current testing schedule appears incomplete. I=
t does not include the first floor, roof cavity, or the large upper deck, an=
d the basement coverage seems partial, given
 the known extent of smoke, water, and chemical contamination.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I therefore request confirmati=
on that the planned inspection and sampling will be expanded to include all l=
evels and relevant structural areas. Alternatively, please confirm that Towe=
r will meet my reasonable costs
 should I need to arrange independent specialists to carry out supplementary=
 testing (including laboratory analysis).</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Please confirm the final timin=
g for the 17th and the revised scope of testing once available.</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Ng=C4=81 mihi,</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Raffaella</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
</div>
