Metson@tower.co.nz">Grant.Metson@tower.co.nz</a>&gt; wrote:</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hel=
lo Raffaella and Abigail,</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Tha=
nk you for the letter received yesterday at 4:35</span><span lang=3D"EN-US">=
</span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I a=
m replying to acknowledge receipt of the letter, and to further acknowledge t=
hat Abigail will be copied into all correspondence moving forward.</span><sp=
an lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I h=
ave requested that the appointed specialists provide dates and times when th=
ey can be available.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I a=
m proposing that the following persons complete site visit, assessing &amp; t=
esting, as a necessary pre-requisite to providing relevant reports for all s=
takeholders to review:</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
