</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=
LBP Builder</span></b><span class=3D"x_apple-converted-space"><span lang=3D"=
EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=3D"EN-US" s=
tyle=3D"font-size:11.0pt">[ unconfirmed individual
 ] =E2=80=93 we will require the builder to cut inspection holes in the wall=
 linings so testing can be completed within the wall cavities.</span><span l=
ang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nb=
sp;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The=
 intention is to test for smoke and chemical contamination within the wall c=
avities, and on the exposed surfaces downstairs. There will be a significant=
 number of sample sites [tests] to
 be completed to be able to author a reliable report. After initial testing i=
s completed, our intention is to apply restorative cleaning methods to targe=
ted individual sample sites, followed by subsequent testing, post-cleaning, t=
o provide data to measure the
 effectiveness of cleaning/decontamination.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></spa=
n></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">All=
 samples taken from site will require laboratory analysis before being incor=
porated into a report. This process may take up to 10 working days =E2=80=93=
 so we want to capture swab samples from surfaces
 before and after the decontamination process is undertaken.</span><span lan=
g=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nb=
sp;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">At t=
his stage we are looking like being able to conduct this testing onsite, as w=
ell as CPEng site visit for assessment, on Friday October 17. Time to yet be=
 confirmed.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nb=
sp;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I a=
m unsure from your letter attached whether Raffaella and/or other nominated p=
arties wish to be present while this testing and assessment is being conduct=
ed. Can you please confirm for me
 so that I can complete arrangements that will suit all parties who need to b=
e present.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"x_MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nb=
sp;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"></span></p>
